## FSM Diagram

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> S_IDLE

    S_IDLE --> S_SET: mode = 1 and enter
    S_IDLE --> S_INPUT: mode = 0 and enter
    S_IDLE --> S_IDLE: no enter

    S_SET --> S_IDLE: enter / save new PIN
    S_SET --> S_SET: wait

    S_INPUT --> S_CHK: enter / capture PIN
    S_INPUT --> S_INPUT: wait

    S_CHK --> S_UNBLK: saved_pin == enter_pin
    S_CHK --> S_BLK: saved_pin != enter_pin

    S_BLK --> S_IDLE: ticks
    S_BLK --> S_BLK: wait

    S_UNBLK --> S_IDLE: enter
    S_UNBLK --> S_UNBLK: wait
